tco\",\"businessType\":\"Indoor Dog Park\",\"description\":\"Petco provides dependable care for Redmond's furry friends. This facility features modern training facilities, caring and attentive team members, offering pet care. Their services creates a safe, dry environment year-round. situated in a prime Redmond location. Experience the difference at Petco\",\"slug\":\"petco\",\"address\":\"7215 170th Ave NE Ste. 115\",\"street\":\"7215 170th Ave NE Ste. 115\",\"city\":\"Redmond\",\"state\":\"WA\",\"zipCode\":\"98052\",\"full_address\":\"7215 170th Ave NE Ste. 115, Redmond, WA 98052, USA\",\"latitude\":47.6687681,\"longitude\":-122.1158301,\"googlePlaceId\":\"ChIJhRoaz7pykFQR3EU-gTknohs\",\"phone\":\"(425) 861-3907\",\"rating\":4.1,\"reviewCount\":531,\"userRatingsTotal\":531,\"photos\":null,\"photo\":null,\"placeTypes\":[\"point_of_interest\",\"establishment\"],\"dataQuality\":\"verified\",\"website\":\"https://stores.petco.com/wa/redmond/pet-supplies-redmond-wa-1218.html\",\"openingHours\":{\"Monday\":\"9:00 AM – 9:00 PM\",\"Tuesday\":\"9:00 AM – 9:00 PM\",\"Wednesday\":\"9:00 AM – 9:00 PM\",\"Thursday\":\"9:00 AM – 9:00 PM\",\"Friday\":\"9:00 AM – 9:00 PM\",\"Saturday\":\"9:00 AM – 9:00 PM\",\"Sunday\":\"10:00 AM – 7:00 PM\"},\"pricing\":{\"pricingSource\":\"unknown\",\"isFree\":false},\"source\":\"static\",\"listingType\":\"free\"},{\"id\":\"ChIJpS2PxN8RkFQRu2B0vty9ACk\",\"name\":\"XL Canine Crates: Stylish, Durable Dog Crates for Large Breeds. Secure Kennels, Spacious Design, Portable Comfort.\",\"businessType\":\"Indoor Dog Park\",\"description\":\"XL Canine Crates: Stylish, Durable Dog Crates for Large Breeds. Secure Kennels, Spacious Design, Portable Comfort. serves the Redmond pet community with dedication. This facility features climate-controlled facilities for Washington's rainy climate, Washington pet care professionals, offering pet care. Their services ensures your dog stays active during Washington's rainy weather. strategically positioned in Redmond.